chigan|Mackinac]]\n|4\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Macomb County, Michigan|Macomb]]\n|2,783\n|165\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Manistee County, Michigan|Manistee]]\n|9\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Marquette County, Michigan|Marquette]]\n|18\n|2\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Mason County, Michigan|Mason]]\n|1\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Mecosta County, Michigan|Mecosta]]\n|9\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Midland County, Michigan|Midland]]\n|28\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Missaukee County, Michigan|Missaukee]]\n|1\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Monroe County, Michigan|Monroe]]\n|165\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Montcalm County, Michigan|Montcalm]]\n|19\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Muskegon County, Michigan|Muskegon]]\n|53\n|4\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Newaygo County, Michigan|Newaygo]]\n|3\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Oakland County, Michigan|Oakland]]\n|4,247\n|246\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Oceana County, Michigan|Oceana]]\n|3\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Ogemaw County, Michigan|Ogemaw]]\n|3\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Osceola County, Michigan|Osceola]]\n|3\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Oscoda County, Michigan|Oscoda]]\n|3\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Otsego County, Michigan|Otsego]]\n|29\n|2\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Ottawa County, Michigan|Ottawa]]\n|59\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Presque Isle County, Michigan|Presque Isle]]\n|1\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Roscommon County, Michigan|Roscommon]]\n|8\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Saginaw County, Michigan|Saginaw]]\n|205\n|7\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Sanilac County, Michigan|Sanilac]]\n|21\n|2\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Schoolcraft County, Michigan|Schoolcraft]]\n|1\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Shiawassee County, Michigan|Shiawassee]]\n|31\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[St. Clair County, Michigan|St. Clair]]\n|162\n|4\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[St. Joseph County, Michigan|St. Joseph]]\n|18\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Tuscola County, Michigan|Tuscola]]\n|36\n|3\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Van Buren County, Michigan|Van Buren]]\n|18\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Washtenaw County, Michigan|Washtenaw]]\n|637\n|15\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Wayne County, Michigan|Wayne]]\n|10,093\n|574\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Wexford County, Michigan|Wexford]]\n|7\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Michigan Department of Corrections|MDOC]]\n|290\n|4\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Out-of-State {{ref label|Note2|b|b}} \n|131\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |Unknown\n|78\n|1\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:right;\" |Total\n! style=\"text-align:right;\" |21,504\n! style=\"text-align:right;\" |1,076\n|-\n|}\n\n<small>Notes:<br>\n{{Note label|Note1|a|a}} Michigan.gov information is updated daily at 3 p.m., with COVID-19 results included as of 10 a.m..<br>\n{{Note label|Note2|b|b}} Patients are not residents, but are being treated within the state of Michigan.</small>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://www.michigan.gov/coronavirus Coronavirus information] from the State of Michigan\n* [https://www.mlive.com/news/jackson/2020/03/updated-maps-michigan-coronavirus-cases-and-exposure-sites.html Updated maps: Michigan coronavirus cases and exposure sites] from MLive.com\n\n{{COVID-19}}\n{{2020 coronavirus pandemic in the United States}}\n{{Portal bar|Coronavirus disease 2019|Medicine|Pandemic|United States|Viruses}}\n\n[[Category:2020 coronavirus pandemic in the United States by state|Michigan]]\n[[Category:2020 in Michigan|coronavirus pandemic]]\n[[Category:Disasters in Michigan]]\n[[Category:Health in Michigan]]\n[[Category:March 2020 events in the United States|coronavirus pandemic]]\n[[Category:April 2020 events in the Unite