abia}} <small>(2015\u201317)</small><ref name=AlJazeeraAmerica/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/syria-rebels-and-tow-missiles-2015-10|title=Saudi Arabia just replenished Syrian rebels with one of the most effective weapons against the Assad regime|publisher=[[Business Insider]] |date=9 October 2015}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Turkey}}<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aa.com.tr/en/turkey/turkish-fm-turkey-supports-free-syrian-army-peshmerga/107563|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120090503/http://www.aa.com.tr/en/turkey/turkish-fm-turkey-supports-free-syrian-army-peshmerga/107563|archivedate=20 November 2015|title=Turkey supports Free Syrian Army|publisher=[[Anadolu Agency]]|date=25 October 2014}}</ref>\n* {{flag|United States}} <small>(2015\u201317)</small><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/13/world/middleeast/syria-russia-airstrikes.html |title=U.S. Weaponry Is Turning Syria into Proxy War With Russia |work=[[The New York Times]] |date=12 October 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/10/airdrops-ammunition-rebels-fighting-isil-syria-151012153543003.html|title=US drops ammunition to rebels fighting ISIL in Syria|publisher=[[Al Jazeera]] |date=13 October 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=U.S. weapons reaching Syrian rebels|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/cia-begins-weapons-delivery-to-syrian-rebels/2013/09/11/9fcf2ed8-1b0c-11e3-a628-7e6dde8f889d_story.html|newspaper=Washington Post|date=11 September 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=U.S. MILITARY WILL LEAVE SYRIA BASE IN DEAL WITH RUSSIA, REPORTS SAY|url=https://www.newsweek.com/us-military-will-give-major-syria-base-deal-russia-reports-say-948272|publisher=Newsweek|date=29 May 2018}}</ref>{{Ref label|america|a}}\n----\n{{flagicon image|Flag of Syrian Democratic Forces.svg}} [[Syrian Democratic Forces]] <small>([[Deir ez-Zor campaign (2017\u201319)#Opening of a second front|2017-2019]])</small><ref>{{cite web|url=https://w