lan-10]]<br />\n[[IAI Searcher|Forpost]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://warfiles.ru/show-109997-forpost-zamechen-v-nebe-nad-siriey.html|title=\"\u0424\u043e\u0440\u043f\u043e\u0441\u0442\" \u0437\u0430\u043c\u0435\u0447\u0435\u043d \u0432 \u043d\u0435\u0431\u0435 \u043d\u0430\u0434 \u0421\u0438\u0440\u0438\u0435\u0439|work=warfiles.ru|accessdate=1 March 2016}}</ref><br />\n'''Ground arms and equipment'''<br />\n'''[[Unmanned ground vehicle|UGV]]'''<br />\nUran-6<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvzvezda.ru/news/vstrane_i_mire/content/201603302207-a6qb.htm|title=\"\u0423\u0440\u0430\u043d-6\" \u0438\u0441\u043f\u043e\u043b\u044c\u0437\u0443\u044e\u0442 \u0440\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0438\u0439\u0441\u043a\u0438\u0435 \u0432\u043e\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044b\u0435 \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0440\u0430\u0437\u043c\u0438\u043d\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044f \u041f\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043c\u0438\u0440\u044b|publisher=|accessdate=2 May 2016}}</ref><br />\n'''[[MRAP]]'''<br />\n[[Kamaz Typhoon]]{{cn|date=February 2020}}<br />\n'''[[Infantry mobility vehicle|IMV]]'''<br />\n[[GAZ Tigr]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sputniknews.com/military/201606131041257462-russia-combat-vehicle-syria/|title=Desert Tiger: Russian-Made Armored Vehicle Well-Proven in Syrian Conflict|last=Sputnik|website=sputniknews.com}}</ref><br />\n[[Iveco LMV|Iveco Rys']]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://defence.ru/editors-choice/pod-palmiru-perebrosili-risi-i-taifuni-dlya-saperov-video/|title=\u041f\u043e\u0434 \u041f\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043c\u0438\u0440\u0443 \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0441\u0438\u043b\u0438 \"\u0420\u044b\u0441\u0438\" \u0438 \"\u0422\u0430\u0439\u0444\u0443\u043d\u044b\" \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0441\u0430\u043f\u0435\u0440\u043e\u0432 (\u0432\u0438\u0434\u0435\u043e)|publisher=}}</ref><br />\n'''[[Short-range ballistic missile|SRBM]]''' (presumed)<br />\n2 [[9K720 Iskander]] (SS-26) missile launchers<ref>[http://www.timesofisrael.com/israeli-satellite-captures-nuclear-capable-russian-missil