P20151001|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120170025/https://www.reuters.com/article/2015/10/01/us-mideast-crisis-syria-turkmen-idUSKCN0RV4FP20151001|archivedate=20 November 2015|title=Syrian Turkmen group says Russian strikes kill over 40 civilians|work=Reuters|accessdate=20 November 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themoscowtimes.com/arts_n_ideas/news/article/syrian-turkmen-group-russian-airstrikes-kill-over-40-civilians/536413.html|title=Syrian Turkmen Group: Russian Airstrikes Kill Over 40 Civilians \u2013 Arts and Ideas|work=The Moscow Times|accessdate=20 November 2015}}</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n{{Portal|Asia|War}}\n* [[List of aviation shootdowns and accidents during the Syrian Civil War]]- That include Russian aircraft lost during the Syrian Civil War.\n* [[Humanitarian aid during the Syrian Civil War#Russia|Humanitarian aid provided by Russia during the War in Syria]]\n* [[Russian Armed Forces casualties in Syria]]\n* [[Timeline of the Syrian Civil War (August\u2013December 2015)]]\n{{clear}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Russian Forces in the Syrian Civil War (2011-present)}}\n* [http://eng.syria.mil.ru/ Russian Ministry of Defence Syria]\n* [http://eng.syria.mil.ru/en/index/syria/news/more.htm?id=12079588@egNews Russian centre for reconciliation of opposing sides in Syria starts issuing everyday bulletin on the course of the reconciliation of opposing sides]\n\n{{Military intervention against ISIL}}\n{{Syrian civil war}}\n{{Russian Conflicts}}\n{{Russia\u2013United States proxy conflict}}\n{{Portal bar|Asia|War}}\n\n[[Category:Russian military intervention in the Syrian Civil War| ]]\n[[Category:2015 in Russia]]\n[[Category:2015 in the Syrian Civil War]]\n[[Category:Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant and Russia]]\n[[Category:Russia\u2013Turkey military relations]]\n[[Category:Iran\u2013Russia military relations]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:Military operati